<figureCitation box="[766,832,1180,1205]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1878,1900]" captionTargetBox="[304,1286,491,1845]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[304,1286,491,1845]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 2. Mecopoda spp. from China. A-C: M. elongata elongata, DE: M. fallax sp. nov., FG: M. niponensis, HI: M. hainanensis sp. nov., J: M. mamorata sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/2640102/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="568">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
